#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:1
msgid "Testing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:5
msgid "Backend tests"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:7
msgid ""
"The backend uses **Jest** with **ts-jest** for TypeScript support and "
"**Supertest** for HTTP integration tests."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:9
msgid ""
"npm test                      # All tests with coverage report\n"
"npm run test:unit             # Unit tests only (tests/unit/)\n"
"npm run test:integration      # Integration tests only (tests/integration/)\n"
"npm run test:watch            # Watch mode — re-runs on file change"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:16
msgid "Unit tests"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:18
msgid ""
"Unit tests cover individual services and middleware in isolation, using Jest "
"mocks for external dependencies (Keycloak JWKS, Operaton API, PostgreSQL)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:20
msgid "Location: `packages/backend/tests/unit/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:22
msgid "Integration tests"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:24
msgid ""
"Integration tests send real HTTP requests to a running Express instance (not "
"a deployed server) and verify the full middleware chain including JWT "
"validation. The test setup uses an in-memory Keycloak mock that issues valid "
"test JWTs."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:26
msgid "Location: `packages/backend/tests/integration/`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:28
msgid "What to test"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:30
msgid "When adding a new route or service:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:31
msgid "Unit test: the service function in isolation (mock all external calls)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:32
msgid ""
"Integration test: the route with a valid JWT → expected response, and with "
"no/invalid JWT → HTTP 401"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:36
msgid "Health check verification"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:38
msgid "The health endpoint is the fastest way to verify a running instance:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:40
msgid ""
"# Local\n"
"curl http://localhost:3002/v1/health | jq .\n"
"\n"
"# ACC\n"
"curl https://acc.api.open-regels.nl/v1/health | jq ."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:48
msgid "Expected healthy response:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:49
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"RONL Business API\",\n"
"  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n"
"  \"environment\": \"development\",\n"
"  \"status\": \"healthy\",\n"
"  \"uptime\": 42.1,\n"
"  \"timestamp\": \"2026-02-20T10:00:00.000Z\",\n"
"  \"services\": {\n"
"    \"keycloak\": { \"status\": \"up\", \"latency\": 45 },\n"
"    \"operaton\": { \"status\": \"up\", \"latency\": 112 }\n"
"  }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:64
msgid ""
"Status values: `healthy` (HTTP 200), `degraded` (HTTP 503 — one or more "
"services down), `unhealthy` (HTTP 503 — health check itself failed)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:68
msgid "Pre-commit and pre-push hooks"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:70
msgid "Husky hooks run automatically:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:72
msgid "**Pre-commit** (via lint-staged):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:73
msgid "ESLint + Prettier on changed `packages/backend/**/*.ts` files"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:74
msgid "ESLint + Prettier on changed `packages/frontend/**/*.{ts,tsx}` files"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:76
msgid "**Pre-push**:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:77
msgid "`npm run type-check` across all workspaces"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:79
msgid ""
"These hooks run before any push reaches CI and catch common issues early."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:83
msgid "CI test run"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:85
msgid "GitHub Actions runs the test suite on every push to `acc` and `main`:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:87
msgid ""
"- name: Run linter\n"
"  working-directory: packages/backend\n"
"  run: npm run lint\n"
"\n"
"- name: Build TypeScript\n"
"  working-directory: packages/backend\n"
"  run: npm run build"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Ctesting.md:97
msgid ""
"A post-deployment health check with 5 retries (10-second intervals) verifies "
"that the deployed instance is responding correctly before the workflow marks "
"the deployment as successful."
msgstr ""
